This is source code for a VR mod for Half-Life. You may use or reuse this code with giving credit.

No warranties whatsoever.

Third party licenses apply where applicable.

VERSION 0.2

Stuff still to do:
[ ] Tracktrain and func_tank controls
[ ] Fix and re-add ladder climbing, jumping and ducking
[ ] Fix yaw rotation in roomscale VR setup
[ ] Add Menu/Intermission/Death room
[ ] Detect levelchange/loading and fix display
[ ] Weapons
[ ]  Make gauss thingy spinnable
[ ]  Make snark reach for left hand
[ ]  Make some nice tripmine placement feature
[ ]  Weapon selection wheel
[ ] Synchronize beam effects for left and right eye

If you want to help, please don't just code ahead and then send a pull request, contact me first and ask what needs outsourcing and how it should be implemented! Had to deny pull requests in the past, because they weren't compatible with other changes I made in the meantime.

====
Hand model based on high poly hand model by Willdabeast and HEV arms textures by JohnChronic: https://gamebanana.com/skins/157391

